OL,5, An 82-year-old man has been found      
OL,6, guilty of the brutal murder of his     
OL,7, ex-wife almost 45 years ago.           
OL,9,FRetired research scientist Christopher 
OL,10,FHarrisson denied killing 32-year-old   
OL,11,FBrenda Page in Aberdeen a year after   
OL,12,Fthe couple were divorced.              
OL,14,FThe body of the genetics expert was    
OL,15,Ffound on her blood-stained bed in her  
OL,16,Fhome on 14 July 1978.                  
OL,18,FA jury convicted Harrisson of the      
OL,19,Fmurder of his ex-wife, who he had told 
OL,20,Fpolice was a "brilliant scientist".    
